{# Executive Summary Template #}
{% extends "base_quarto.j2" %}

{% block content %}

## {{ headline | default("Key Insights", true) }}

{{ insight | default("This executive summary provides actionable insights from the latest refugee data.", true) }}

## Key Statistics

{% if statistics %}
| Metric | Value | Trend |
|--------|-------|-------|
{% for stat in statistics %}
| {{ stat.metric }} | {{ stat.value }} | {{ stat.trend | default("Stable", true) }} |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
| Total Refugees | {{ total_refugees | default("N/A", true) }} | {{ trend | default("Stable", true) }} |
| New Displacements | {{ new_displacements | default("N/A", true) }} | {{ new_trend | default("Stable", true) }} |
| Returns | {{ returns | default("N/A", true) }} | {{ return_trend | default("Stable", true) }} |
{% endif %}

## Impact Highlights

{% if impacts %}
{% for impact in impacts %}
### {{ impact.title }}
{{ impact.description }}

- **Affected**: {{ impact.affected | default("N/A", true) }}
- **Severity**: {{ impact.severity | default("Moderate", true) }}
- **Response**: {{ impact.response | default("Ongoing", true) }}

{% endfor %}
{% else %}
### Humanitarian Impact
Significant humanitarian needs identified in {{ region | default("multiple regions", true) }}.

- **Affected**: {{ affected_population | default("Thousands", true) }}
- **Severity**: {{ severity | default("High", true) }}
- **Response**: {{ response_status | default("Active", true) }}

### Host Community Impact
Host communities facing increased pressure from refugee inflows.

- **Affected**: {{ host_communities | default("Multiple", true) }}
- **Severity**: {{ host_severity | default("Moderate", true) }}
- **Response**: {{ host_response | default("Support needed", true) }}
{% endif %}

## Call to Action

{% if call_to_action %}
{% for action in call_to_action %}
- **{{ action.priority }}**: {{ action.description }}
  - **Target**: {{ action.target | default("Immediate", true) }}
  - **Resources**: {{ action.resources | default("Required", true) }}

{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- **Urgent**: Increase funding for emergency response
  - **Target**: Immediate
  - **Resources**: ${{ funding_needed | default("5M", true) }}

- **High**: Strengthen host community support
  - **Target**: 3 months
  - **Resources**: Partnerships required

- **Medium**: Enhance data collection
  - **Target**: 6 months
  - **Resources**: Technical support needed
{% endif %}

## Strategic Recommendations

{% if recommendations %}
{% for recommendation in recommendations %}
### {{ recommendation.title }}
{{ recommendation.description }}

**Benefits**:
- {{ recommendation.benefits | join("\n- ") | default("Improved outcomes", true) }}

**Implementation**:
- **Timeline**: {{ recommendation.timeline | default("3-6 months", true) }}
- **Resources**: {{ recommendation.resources | default("To be determined", true) }}

{% endfor %}
{% else %}
### Enhance Response Capacity
Strengthen UNHCR's ability to respond to emerging crises.

**Benefits**:
- Faster deployment
- Better coordination
- Improved outcomes

**Implementation**:
- **Timeline**: 3-6 months
- **Resources**: Additional staff and funding

### Improve Data Quality
Enhance data collection and analysis capabilities.

**Benefits**:
- More accurate reporting
- Better trend analysis
- Improved decision making

**Implementation**:
- **Timeline**: 6-12 months
- **Resources**: Technical expertise and tools
{% endif %}

{% endblock %}